## 5. Conclusion
The T20 EDA Dashboard transcends standard cricket scorekeeping. By meticulously isolating World Cup scenarios and calculating nuanced metrics—such as Scoreboard Pressure, Wicket Quality, and Partnership Dependency—the project highlights the complex strategies underlying the T20 format. The fusion of Python data tools with a premium interactive frontend demonstrates a modern approach to sports analytics, making elite-level scouting metrics accessible and visually compelling.

