## 6. Future Scope
Continuing the evolution of this project, future iterations aim to integrate Predictive Machine Learning. Preliminary explorations into **CatBoost** and **XGBoost** algorithms promise the capability to implement a live Win Probability Predictor. This model would evaluate live match conditions—current run rate, target score, remaining wickets, and historical venue behavior—to accurately forecast the match outcome dynamically, while providing users with Feature Importance charts to understand the "why" behind the algorithm's predictions.
